_sText:
Hi!

I have been working on this map for 3 days, and I should tell it's finally done.

So, it's an AIM themed map with Deagle and 16 player slots, also three he-granades placed, two at the top of the stairs and one in middle at the bridge. I used custom textures for better in-game experience, they are made be my of course. I hope you guys like the idea, and you'll enjoy playing on this map.
Also write some comments & rate. :)
